  "2026-04-06T16:46:36.539Z",codex-agent,"Reopened for 13-issue remediation wave after duplicate-check sweep (pm context --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 30; pm list-in-progress --limit 30; pm search 'comments-audit full-history latest row_count latest 0' --limit 10). Follow-up scope: keep --full-history/--latest exclusivity, align help/contracts/docs wording accordingly, make export.row_count deterministic numeric across modes, and define --latest 0 as explicit summary-only behavior with tests."
  "2026-04-06T17:19:29.337Z",codex-agent,"Progress: comments-audit hardening now keeps --full-history and --latest mutually exclusive across runtime/help/contracts/completion wording, makes export.row_count deterministic in latest/full_history modes, and formalizes --latest 0 as summary-only (items returned with comment_count but empty comments arrays). Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/comments-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed."
  "2026-04-06T18:47:15.234Z",codex-agent,"Completed comments-audit semantics hardening: latest/full-history exclusivity guidance, deterministic export metadata, and valid --latest 0 summary-only behavior. Help/contracts/tests/docs were synchronized across CLI and Pi surfaces. Verification: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage."
  "2026-04-06T19:39:55.029Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence refreshed via pm context/list/search sweep. Reusing this task for additive comments-audit top-level governance summary metrics (totals, zero-comment counts, coverage, by-type breakdown) with deterministic output and regression coverage."
